"Logical separation within your nova deployment for physical isolation or "
"redundancy."
msgstr ""
"物理的な隔離や冗長性のために、Nova デプロイメントの中で論理的な分離が必要な場"
"合。"

#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/ch_arch_scaling.xml:214
